Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:58.20,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}烈焰啊 燃盡我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.43,0:01:06.62,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}想用熊熊燃燒的胸懷抱緊你 這不是罪孽吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:13.60,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}用烈焰驅散黑暗 CHOIR JAIL 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.96,0:01:19.17,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自哀之人怎能唱出夢想之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:25.19,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}站在原地嘶吼“到底誰能給我答案？”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:29.66,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}抬起頭來才能察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.13,0:01:35.91,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你的瞳孔中有著我尋覓已久的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:41.15,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}如果奇跡指向這一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.54,0:01:43.87,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}拭去盈眶的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:46.41,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}向前大步前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:51.24,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}解放我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.35,0:01:56.95,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在如此的煉獄中會迷失前進的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:02:02.05,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}烈焰啊 燃盡我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.41,0:02:10.08,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}化為一道烈焰逝向彼方 這渾身的炙熱不是罪孽吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:17.31,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}用烈焰驅散黑暗 CHOIR JAIL 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:16.01,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ひとりきりのさびしさ　ひとときのほほえみ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:23.95,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたがくれるものは　みんないとしい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.69,0:22:33.64,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すぐそばにいても　触れられないもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.18,0:22:42.54,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心は月のように　形をかえていくの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.04,0:22:51.10,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,かなわない約束も　かわかない涙も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:23:02.03,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたがくれたものは　だきしめておどる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:16.01,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人的孤獨 一時間的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:23.95,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為我帶來的瑰寶 一樣樣都令人愛不釋手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.69,0:22:33.64,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕兩人之間的距離觸手可及 可無形之壁註定你我天人永隔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.18,0:22:42.54,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心宛如明月 陰晴圓缺不斷變幻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.04,0:22:51.10,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定依舊無法實現 眼淚仍然不願乾涸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:23:02.03,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能把你給的瑰寶 緊擁懷中驀然舞起..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.33,0:00:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.62,0:00:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.74,0:00:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛苦..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧江同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.18,0:00:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 最近都不來部室 還以為妳退部了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.11,0:00:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新谷同學請假之後第一次來這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.52,0:00:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小..小此木
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又..消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.90,0:02:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪之九 怨念少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.13,0:02:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？遵命遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 貞一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎..怎麼啦啊 夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.21,0:02:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼呀 就是要緊緊抱著你而已呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高興嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.57,0:02:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？這..這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你喜歡我對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為..我喜歡夕子學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說 那個是騙人的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..不是騙人的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再說一次給我聽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次對我說你喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不出來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不願說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就說呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快~一~點~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是..是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡妳..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再大聲一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡妳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡妳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.35,0:03:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一口氣！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對夕子學姐..！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧江同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在玩什麼相聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼相聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是要緊的時候 妳不要來亂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.41,0:03:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子才是 一大早就擋著校門
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:03:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳才是來亂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還真是不覺得厭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三百六十五天都在那卿卿我我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不扯這些 新谷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於昨天的事..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走 貞一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子..生氣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說貞一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你這樣一聲不應很無聊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在考試
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是考試中哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關係大著了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 繼續剛才那個話題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說你喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不說給我聽的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把試卷的答案說出來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:04:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以跑去看正確答案的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.12,0:05:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,0:05:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60}喜歡妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？只有這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs70}最喜歡妳了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 用嘴巴說出聲來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後我們再慢慢說吧 貞一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想這樣蒙混過關對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:30.25,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}測驗時間 40分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面的人 把答案紙收起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等..等一下！
