Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢調戲老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什麼呀你！
